<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body style="background-color:#ccc;">
	<div id="container" style="background-color:#e7e7e8;padding-bottom:60px;">
		<h1 class="logo" style="font-weight:bold;text-align:center;font-size:72px;font-variant:small-caps;letter-spacing:0.08em;color: #000;font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; margin-bottom:30px;">zalpe</h1>
			<div id="content" style="width:80%;padding:60px;background-color:#fff;margin:0px auto 60px;">
			
			
				<h4>Dear <%= @sellername %>,</h4>
<div class="mailbody" style="padding:30px;background-color:#e1e1e1;">
	<p>Greetings from Phonesalad!</p>
	<p>We thank you for listing your phone with Phonesalad. Your phone has been sold. This email contains your order summary. Please meetup/ship or take necessary action to complete your part of the order.
	Please find below the summary of your order at phonesalad.com:</p>
	<h4>Order details table</h4>
	<table class="table table-bordered">
		<tr><th>Orderno</th><th>Item</th><th>Price</th><th>Quantity</th>
		</tr>
		<tr><td><%= @order.id%></td><td><%= @order.devicename %></td><td><%= @order.ordertotal%></td><td>1</td>
			
		
			</tr>
	</table><br/><br/>
	<% if @listing.deliveryby == "pickup" %>
	<h3>Pickup Address</h3>
	<p><%= @listing.pickupaddress %></p>
	<% elsif @listing.deliveryby == "courier"  %>
	<p>Your phone will be shipped to you by <%= Time.now.to_date + 2 %></p>
	<h3>Shipping Address:</h3>
	<p>
	<%= @order.shipping_address %>
	</p>
	<br/><br/>
	<p>
	<% end %>
	
	
	Go to your <a href="www.phonesalad.com/pages/dashboard">dashboard</a> to see more info about the order.
	Please contact us should you have any questions or need further assistance.
	Thank you for shopping with us!</p>
</div>

	<p>Thanks and Regards,</p>
	<p><a href="http://www.phonesalad.com">Phonesalad Team</a></p>   

	</div>
	</div>
  </body>
</html>


